    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/19f494d36d11e98aae83036a6d986f62.avif?t=1772147406\" width=1600 height=426 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>设想这样一个地方：所有失落与被遗忘的东西都会汇聚于此——破旧的玩具、泛黄的信件、孤独的袜子。遗忘之地正是这样一个神奇的世界，栖息着遗忘族——由遗失物品化身而成的奇异生灵，它们都怀着重新被世人铭记的深切渴望。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Forgotlings》是一款电影级的剧情导向动作冒险作品，</strong>你将化身菲格——一个曾被世人遗忘的人体模型，如今已成为拥有自主意识的光明战舰沃拉雷的舰长。当黑暗势力蠢蠢欲动，古老的仇恨撕裂大地时，你必须驾船翱翔于风暴席卷的天际和废墟城市之上，将敌对的部族重新凝聚，阻止整个世界走向毁灭。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚔️ 游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>体验手绘动画奇迹：</strong> 感受数千帧精雕细琢的逐帧手绘动画与绝美风景画卷，让遗忘之地跃然纸上，每个瞬间都如同置身动画大片之中。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/5f16d8ea23ca1eb82482177c706c9b03.avif?t=1772147406\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras_big/5f16d8ea23ca1eb82482177c706c9b03.avif?t=1772147406 width=1600 height=224 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>利剑与语言的艺术：</strong> 以雄辩之词说服遗忘族加入你的阵营，以钢铁之刃守护村落免遭盗匪侵扰，通过INA——这款在破碎世界中维系团结的珍贵桌游——化解纷争。  </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>策略性战斗系统：</strong> 要么正面强攻展开酣畅淋漓的近战厮杀，要么潜伏暗影施展致命偷袭。在与遗忘之地各族建立深厚情谊的过程中解锁强大能力。特设故事模式，专为注重剧情体验的玩家量身打造。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/b795efda717101e1347bdf0c1f6b1679.poster.avif?t=1772147406\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/b795efda717101e1347bdf0c1f6b1679.webm?t=1772147406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/b795efda717101e1347bdf0c1f6b1679.mp4?t=1772147406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索原创奇幻世界：</strong> 驾驶有生命的战舰沃拉雷畅游遗忘之地，赢得五大遗忘族部族的信任与敬重。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/a7c4c6b2d12c2ec9aeffa53ede9d6649.poster.avif?t=1772147406\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/a7c4c6b2d12c2ec9aeffa53ede9d6649.webm?t=1772147406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/a7c4c6b2d12c2ec9aeffa53ede9d6649.mp4?t=1772147406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>抉择塑造命运：</strong> 你的每个决定都将影响菲格的人生轨迹和人际关系网络，最终左右整个遗忘之地的兴衰存亡。运用独创的对话轮盘系统应对紧张局面——或者来一局精彩的INA对弈来化解剑拔弩张的氛围，这是一款融合了国际象棋与围棋精髓的策略佳作。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/4c58ab2921b9f0aeaf5115aa994e818b.poster.avif?t=1772147406\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/4c58ab2921b9f0aeaf5115aa994e818b.webm?t=1772147406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/4c58ab2921b9f0aeaf5115aa994e818b.mp4?t=1772147406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>INA棋艺对决：</strong> 凭借智慧化解危机四伏的遭遇——或通过一场巧妙的INA博弈来舒缓紧绷的神经，这是一款汲取了国际象棋和围棋灵感的策略性桌游。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉醉于震撼音效：</strong> 全明星阵容配音团队与国际知名合唱团体“声音剧场”倾力打造的动人乐章，精心雕琢的音频设计将你冒险历程中的每一次情感起伏都演绎得淋漓尽致。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/0cc99b1dabae959054b990ac1d6a3c86.poster.avif?t=1772147406\" width=1080 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/0cc99b1dabae959054b990ac1d6a3c86.webm?t=1772147406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌍 深度世界观构建</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>遗忘之地：</strong>一个充满魔力的国度，在这里失落的物品——遗忘族——觉醒了自我意识，其中一些还残留着前世生活的朦胧回忆，如今都在寻找存在的意义与归属。为这个四分五裂的世界带去希望与救赎的曙光。 </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🚩 The Forgotling Tribes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结识栖居于遗忘之地的五大遗忘族部族。从博学求知的维德拉族到勤劳进取的奥费罗族，每个部族都以其独特的人生哲学和悠久历史为你的旅程增添丰富的视角与挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/5e96061072409dbebbe42ac65367dbe5.avif?t=1772147406\" width=1600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>维德拉族：</strong>博学的智者与知识的守护者，定居于逝昔公园。他们深信解读过往是开创未来的钥匙，矢志不渝地探寻天地间的一切奥秘。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/6f5344e9ebbd2af3d751813c747452e3.avif?t=1772147406\" width=1600 height=400 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>奥费罗族：</strong>来自瞭望镇的革新先锋与工程巨匠，专注于推动进步与技术革命，即便要以牺牲传统为代价。他们改造周遭环境与社会结构，通过不断的进步与创新铸就崭新的未来。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/5b33612c2c8fdbc53949b1cef97d8199.avif?t=1772147406\" width=1600 height=400 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>塞尔武斯族：</strong>塞尔武斯族将服务他人视为天职，在守护和提升同胞的过程中找到人生价值。他们安居于庇护岛，将慈悲为怀奉为信条，常被誉为这片土地上共情之心的化身。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/b7fc4d5d7659e008843ddb2de0bbda99.avif?t=1772147406\" width=1600 height=400 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>索纳维族：</strong>来自瀑布地区的无畏探险家，立志要绘制出连通遗忘之地每一个角落的完整地图。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/f36c3318b26e6c8b9c86dc83e6ffd715.avif?t=1772147406\" width=1600 height=400 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>卡鲁斯族：</strong>红树林深处的神秘灵修者。卡鲁斯族追求超脱物质束缚的终极觉悟，渴望与灵气洪流——遗忘之地的生命源泉——融为一体。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⛵️ 遗忘之地的其他住民</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>盗匪与异端者：</strong>这些遗忘族拒绝接受部族派系的条条框框，在荒野中闯出属于自己的道路，为一己私利而行，时刻挑战着既有的秩序。 </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>巨兽：</strong>威胁着遗忘之地根基的神秘力量化身。  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/61594a58e5cd3c2bb8b6578a1639b7b4.poster.avif?t=1772147406\" width=1600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/61594a58e5cd3c2bb8b6578a1639b7b4.webm?t=1772147406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2059570/extras/61594a58e5cd3c2bb8b6578a1639b7b4.mp4?t=1772147406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🛠️ 开发心路历程</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Forgotlings》是独立游戏工作室Throughline Games历时五年精心雕琢的心血结晶，在其前作《Forgotton Anne》这一获奖佳作奠定的坚实基础上更进一步。游戏在热情洋溢的玩家社群鼎力支持下，通过Kickstarter众筹平台获得成功，这充分体现了大家对制作团队在叙事艺术与视觉美学方面愿景的由衷认同。</p>",
